{%- comment -%} Custom Liquid blok – vlož v buy boxu pod Description (nebo jako samostatný blok). {%- endcomment -%}
<div class="fitka-love">
  <h3 class="fitka-love__h">Proč si ho zamiluješ</h3>
  <ul class="fitka-love__list">
    <li class="fitka-love__item">
      <span class="fitka-love__ic" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 3l7 3v5c0 4.5-3 8-7 10-4-2-7-5.5-7-10V6l7-3Z"/></svg></span>
      <span>Spolehlivé krytí vpředu i vzadu – nikde nic neprosvítá.</span>
    </li>
    <li class="fitka-love__item">
      <span class="fitka-love__ic" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.5 19 2c1 2.5 1.5 7-1 11a7 7 0 0 1-7 7Z"/><path d="M2 22c1.5-3 3.5-5 6-7"/></svg></span>
      <span>Antibakteriální bambusová vložka pro svěžest po celý den.</span>
    </li>
    <li class="fitka-love__item">
      <span class="fitka-love__ic" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 12s3.5-7 10-7 10 7 10 7-3.5 7-10 7S2 12 2 12Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2.5"/><path d="m3 3 18 18"/></svg></span>
      <span>Neviditelné pod oblečením – žádné rýhy ani švy.</span>
    </li>
    <li class="fitka-love__item">
      <span class="fitka-love__ic" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg></span>
      <span>Drží na místě, netlačí a neroluje se – ani po pár kilometrech.</span>
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>
<style>
  .fitka-love{ margin:22px 0 0; }
  .fitka-love__h{ font-size:1.2rem; margin:0 0 12px; color:#393939; }
  .fitka-love__list{ list-style:none; margin:0; padding:0; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px; }
  .fitka-love__item{ display:flex; gap:12px; align-items:flex-start; }
  .fitka-love__ic{ flex:0 0 auto; color:#a0304e; margin-top:1px; }
  .fitka-love__item span:last-child{ color:#393939; font-size:.95rem; line-height:1.35; }
</style>
